summary: Unicorn store, starring Brie Larson AND DIRECTED BY Brie Larson! Made me cry because never have I heard the message that your...
body: Unicorn store, starring Brie Larson AND DIRECTED BY Brie Larson! Made me cry because never have I heard the message that your failures can be something to take pride in. Because bro if you failed that means you put the effort and found the strength to TRY, and I hate glitter but when Brie Larson threw it in the air and said these are all my problems that I’m gonna vacuum away… hoes you better believe for a hot minute glitter wasn’t the worst and neither were my problems.

summary: I just finished Unicorn Store and it is so beautiful and pure and it’s energy is just... wow. I love Kit and her aura and I want...
body:
I just finished Unicorn Store and it is so beautiful and pure and it’s energy is just… wow. I love Kit and her aura and I want her to be happy for ever. The movie was amazing, I loved Virgils character, I loved Samuel L. Jackson, I loved the concept, I loved the message, I FUCKING CRIED WITH HER SPEECH IN THE END, OKAY?

I get that it’s not a movie for everybody but I still think everyone should give it a chance.
